data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous home located in much sought after Hopyard Farms.  Features a first floor office, sunroom, beautiful back deck and 4 bedrooms upstairs, including a large master bedroom with a huge walk in closet and lovely master bath. If you need more space, the basement is partially finished. Enjoy all the amenities of Hopyard Farms with community pool, playgrounds and community center.  Easy commute to Dahlgren area or Fredericksburg.
